## âš–ï¸ **Traditional Datacenter vs Cloud (Comparison)**

| Feature              | Traditional Datacenter              | Cloud (Consumption-Based Model)    |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Cost                 | High upfront CapEx                  | Pay-as-you-go OpEx                 |
| Maintenance          | You manage hardware, power, cooling | Cloud provider manages it          |
| Scalability          | Difficult and slow                  | Instant scaling up or down         |
| Resource Utilization | Often underused                     | Fully optimized â€“ pay only for use |
| Flexibility          | Limited                             | Highly flexible                    |

