## ğŸš€ **Benefits of the Consumption-Based Model**

âœ… **No upfront costs** â€” start instantly without buying servers.
âœ… **No wasted capacity** â€” pay only for whatâ€™s used.
âœ… **Scalable** â€” add or remove resources anytime.
âœ… **Predictable costs** â€” easy to monitor and control.
âœ… **Efficient operations** â€” focus on business, not infrastructure.

